{"tid":2393392,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"王家衛監製《出貓特攻隊》導演新作　《一杯上路》辛丹斯電影節獲評審團特別獎","createTime":"2021-02-03T11:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T12:22:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb494792f3f600ed3d0fba135113eb2b01db953d","tid":2393392,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"王家衛監製、《出貓特攻隊》導演納塔屈彭皮里亞（Baz Poonpiriya）執導的電影《一杯上路》（One For The Road），入圍辛丹斯電影節（Sundance Film Festival）的世界電影競賽單元，並獲得該單元評審團特別獎。<br />\n<br />\n影片由泰劇《新鐵石心腸》男星Tor Thanapob、《戀愛病發》的Violette Wautier、《出貓特攻隊》Aokbab Chutimon等主演，這次也是Aokbab Chutimon繼《出貓特攻隊》後，再與導演納塔屈彭皮里亞合作。<br />\n<br />\n《一杯上路》以青春、友情為題，聚焦一對好兄弟，跨越14萬公里，進行一場有笑有淚的另類告別之旅。為了呈現電影中跨越14萬公里的約定，影片橫跨兩大洲，在紐約、曼谷、芭提雅、清邁等5地實地取景。<br />\n<br />\n王家衛從劇本到拍攝的全程指導參與，他談到與納塔屈彭皮里亞合作說：「Baz極有才華，好開心有機會與他合作，他有獨特強大的講故事技巧，之前在《出貓特攻隊》已表露無遺。」<br />\n<br />\n至於導演Baz則笑言作為電影工作者，必須離開舒適圈才有進步，能與王家衛導演合作正是脫離舒適區， 保留初心開拓導演新視野的最好機會。"},{"pid":"a41993510fc9cffdf69ccc7411d72dc6e4e3c93e","tid":2393392,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:05:41.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"efedb0f69f0fa4855c4ee9ab3791eacc07679d81","tid":2393392,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XGdsRJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGdsRJE.jpg&h=5aa68660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqvfgak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbqvfgak.jpg&h=d9db1431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2RVgam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2RVgam.jpg&h=1ff7557e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rXA0B2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rXA0B2.jpg&h=4fa2a1dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WXUwJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WXUwJJ.jpg&h=3bb6ff4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qcw943K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcw943K.jpg&h=5d2535af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NvS5DoL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvS5DoL.jpg&h=bdece45f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}